{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Description\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Apply a positive or negative delay to up to two audio channel in a track and optionally to Midi\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 modes:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Stereo: All Sliders are coupled\par}
