{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Enables a standard three button wheel mouse to be used as a MIDI controller. To use: Place the mouse cursor over FX graphics window. Use mouse wheel or click (middle button) and drag to send continuous output Use left or right buttons to send momentary output.\par}
}

